narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes, the resources available to me were adequate for fulfillment of the assigned work.
I found the resources to be adequate.
The resources given to us were more than adequate. I really appreciated the session we had at the maps library, as it really broadened my view on the resources available to me at the university.
